sentences.sentence: Those symptoms included high LH and testosterone levels, irregular reproductive cycles, and fewer ovulations.
sentences.translation: 那些症状包括高黄体生成素和睾酮水平、不规则的生殖周期和排卵减少。

sentences.sentence: Canines are considered one of the more difficult mammals to clone because of their reproductive cycle that includes difficult-to-predict ovulations.
sentences.translation: 犬类被视为较难复制的一种哺乳类动物，因为它们的繁殖周期中包含了难以预测的排卵过程。
